      <title>英国房价今年初创 20 个月来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/uk-house-prices-start-the-year-with-biggest-rise-in-20-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rightmove 数据显示，2025 年初，英国房屋要价出现一年半以来的最大涨幅，表明房地产市场信心坚挺。]]></description>
